replies.body:
We don't need your condescending "stupid ass" preaching your nonsense here. I couldn't care less for suggestions. I'm not getting payed to offer fixes, and I'm sure as hell not rewarded with good gameplay either for the past year minimum.. Not to mention Riot's not doing its part towards players. No, more dumb skins and bundles, dumb decal emblems/emotes and more ways to take money from the consumer, are not being done for the playerbase that's for damn sure.

I sure as hell am not going to offer any bloody fixes when this shit ships to live straight out of PBE without any sort of player feedback being taken into account, when communication is second to none towards the community, when their policies are cancer, and when their player-support is second to worst only surpassed by Steam.
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
